        <div class="question"> 
            <h3>Question 9</h3>
            <ul>A: You've been authorised to share 
                the information the charity is requesting, so send over the entire file</ul>
            <ul>B: Encrypt the file before sending the entire document over</ul>
            <ul>C: Inform the charity that their isn't an 
                appropriate method of sharing the information they've requested</ul>
            <ul>D: Seek further authorisation permission from your line manager</ul>
            <ul>E: Send only the information the charity requires rather than the whole file</ul>
        
            <p>Answer: E</p>
        </div>

        <div class="question"> 
            <h3>Question 10</h3>
            <ul>A: Shutdown your computer every time you leave your desk</ul>
            <ul>B: Ensure that sensitive or personal material is securely locked away</ul>
            <ul>C: Always lock removable media, such as external hard drives or SD cards</ul>
            <ul>D: Keep passwords memorable and similar to one another</ul>
            <ul>E: You don't need to keep a clear desk when working at home or remotely</ul>
        
